title: Seaside Snacks & Shacks
overview: Sabin Lomac, a native of Maine and a lobster roll expert, is in search of the country's most decadent and delicious eats by the seaside. From Long Island, New York to Seaside Heights, New Jersey to Milwaukee, Wisconsin to Rockport, Massachusetts, Lomac is diving into some of the most unforgettable dishes along the shores including crab cake and bacon grilled cheese sandwiches and creamy clam chowder with puffer pork skin. Sabin will sink his teeth into all the delicious dishes making waves on Seaside Snacks & Shacks.
